            <div class="title">
                Sentenced Soldier, Germany
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1950-06-28/debates/9edc3faf-f589-4e69-96ec-572d689aafef/MiscellaneousFinancialProvisionsBill" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
