        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-42e3b392-8985-4f0d-ad1a-03efc0693f7a">
                Mr. Strachey
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-42e3b392-8985-4f0d-ad1a-03efc0693f7a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-06-28/debates/76591247-2447-4a30-a4eb-d450c7e194be/SentencedSoldierGermany#contribution-42e3b392-8985-4f0d-ad1a-03efc0693f7a">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I am obliged to my right hon. Friend for that question. Yes, the courts martial proceedings were fully open to the public as a whole.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-42e3b392-8985-4f0d-ad1a-03efc0693f7a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
